MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Consolidates component-preview (:5173) and screen-preview (:5175) into
the single generated/ Vite server (:5174). Screens live at
generated/src/pages/, components at generated/src/components/{id}/,
with preview routes at /__preview/{id} and /__theme-preview.

- scaffold: adds pages/, assets/, hooks/, services/, utils/, types/,
  styles/ dirs; writes App.tsx with DarkModeManager + NavigationListener;
  removes component-preview and screen-preview scaffolding entirely
- dev-server-manager: removes preview and screens server slots; only
  runner slot remains
- navigation: syncGeneratedRouter discovers pages/ and components/,
  generates router.tsx with page routes + /__preview/{id} routes
- panels: ComponentsPanel, ScreensPanel, ThemesPanel all use runnerUrl
  and write directly into generated/src/
- prompts: components now use export default function + explicit imports
  instead of the old global/no-import style
- SidebarRail: new screens/components write placeholder code into
  generated/src/pages/ and generated/src/components/ respectively
- projectSettingsStore: removes devServerPort and screensPreviewPort

